Shadow Hand (Stance)
Level: Swordsage 5, Saint 5
Prerequisite: Two Shadow Hand maneuvers
Initiation Action: 1 swift action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Stance; Special <i>see text</i>

While you are in this stance, your speed drops to one third of its normal value and you gain a +2 bonus to dexterity.  After you end this stance, if you are equipped with a Shadow Hand weapon, for one round your speed drops to two thirds of its normal value and you gain a +8 bonus to dexterity.